{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"floral-flute-sepal","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n\n1. Sync a rebar store to Jira (e.g. the REB cutover) where local tickets have\n   assignees that are not Jira users (agent names like `claude`, `claude-opus`).\n2. Run `rebar reconcile --mode dry-run` after the initial create pass.\n\n## Expected vs Actual\n\n- **Expected:** once a ticket is created+bound and its synced fields match, the\n  reconciler emits no further mutations for it (convergence).\n- **Actual:** ~323 of 355 bound tickets emit an `assignee` update every pass. The\n  local assignee (e.g. `claude`) is not a Jira user, so the applier soft-fails the\n  assign (`assignee 'claude' cannot be assigned — retrying without assignee`),\n  Jira stays unassigned, and `_assignee_matches(\"claude\", None)` is False — so the\n  differ re-emits the same assignee update on the next pass. Perpetual churn (passes\n  still succeed; the canary stays green — this is noise/inefficiency, not failure).\n\n## Root cause\n\n`outbound_differ._diff_fields` + `_assignee_matches`: a local assignee that cannot\nbe resolved to a Jira account never matches Jira's (unassigned) state, and there is\nno \"unresolvable assignee → don't re-emit\" suppression after the applier soft-fails.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] A bound ticket whose local assignee cannot be assigned in Jira does NOT\n      re-emit an assignee update every pass (converge or suppress-after-soft-fail).\n- [ ] Decide the intended semantics: skip assignee sync for non-Jira-user\n      assignees, map agent identities to a service account, or record an\n      unresolvable-assignee marker so the differ stops re-emitting.\n- [ ] A dry-run after convergence shows 0 perpetual assignee-only updates.","id":"9b94-af9e-4acf-4dff","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":["jira-sync","reconciler","convergence"],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"Reconciler churns assignee updates for non-Jira-user assignees (never converges)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782430472307427001,"uuid":"440aed01-4a7e-44d8-9e7b-a8c54f9b1430"}